{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/national-space-operations-centre/about/about-our-services","content_id":"a0b82662-d846-43c2-b912-3a3f9d29fa97","description":"The National Space Operations Centre develops and operates the UK’s space surveillance and protection capabilities.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>NSpOC provides warning and protection services primarily to UK-licensed satellite operators and government departments.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"our-mission-sets-include\">Our mission sets include:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>protecting and defending the UK’s space interests</li>\n  <li>missile warning</li>\n  <li>uncontrolled re-entry early warning</li>\n  <li>in-space collision avoidance</li>\n  <li>fragmentation alerting and monitoring</li>\n  <li>support to licence monitoring</li>\n  <li>space weather notifications and advice</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Publicly available space weather notifications are provided by the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.metoffice.gov.uk/weather/learn-about/space-weather/met-office-role\" class=\"govuk-link\">Met Office</a>.</p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.monitor-your-satellites.service.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\">Monitor Your Satellites</a> is available to registered users (UK-licensed satellite operators)</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2024-05-16T08:58:58Z"}],"organisation":"6b681c1a-a04b-40fa-bddd-d331c2f730e2","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about_our_services","first_published_at":"2024-05-16T09:58:58+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/national-space-operations-centre/about/about-our-services","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/national-space-operations-centre/about/about-our-services","base_path":"/government/organisations/national-space-operations-centre/about/about-our-services","content_id":"a0b82662-d846-43c